snippet.title: First 5 Hours in Life is Feudal: MMO
snippet.description:
To ease your medieval growing pains, we’re making  an introductory guide for players. Off we go, fasten your leather seatbelts and get ready, it’s now time for your FIRST FIVE HOURS IN LIFE IS FEUDAL.

Begin your feudal journey: https://play.lifeisfeudal.com/
Like us on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/lifeisfeudal/
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/LifeisFeudal
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/lifeisfeudalofficial/
